OL,3,CHow 2022's 'alarming' unrest shook
OL,4,CLeicester's proud harmony
OL,6,FLeicester has always been proud of its
OL,7,Freputation as a multicultural city
OL,8,Fwhere various communities have co-
OL,9,Fexisted for decades without any major
OL,10,Fproblems.
OL,12,FIn the early 1970s, when the city was
OL,13,Fvery different to the way it is now,
OL,14,Fthere was some apprehension from local
OL,15,Fresidents about the arrival of
OL,16,Fthousands of people from Uganda.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
