OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1771967127
OL,3,CHow 2022's 'alarming' unrest shook
OL,4,CLeicester's proud harmony
OL,6,FWhile there were no riots, far-right
OL,7,Fgroups were hostile towards the new
OL,8,Farrivals, and the City Council even
OL,9,Fplaced an advert in a Ugandan
OL,10,Fnewspaper telling Asians not to come
OL,11,Fto Leicester as 'there were no jobs
OL,12,Fand no houses'.
OL,14,FFortunately, the warnings were ignored.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
