OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1771967127
OL,3,CHow 2022's 'alarming' unrest shook
OL,4,CLeicester's proud harmony
OL,6,FFamilies came, with very little money
OL,7,Fbut lots of hope. They not only
OL,8,Fintegrated but thrived. Some of the
OL,9,Fnew arrivals from Uganda and Kenya
OL,10,Fstarted their own businesses and
OL,11,Fbreathed new life into Belgrave, now
OL,12,Fthe heart of the Asian community in
OL,13,FLeicester.
OL,15,FA fading Industrial area, in a state
OL,16,Fof decline, was transformed into the
OL,17,Fdazzling Golden Mile, renowned for its
OL,18,Fjewellery shops, restaurants and
OL,19,Fcultural vibrancy.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
