OL,3,CHow 2022's 'alarming' unrest shook
OL,4,CLeicester's proud harmony
OL,6,FOver the next 50 years, the South
OL,7,FAsian population, made up of Hindus
OL,8,Fand Muslims grew. They lived and
OL,9,Fworked side-by-side.
OL,11,FAs a young Hindu man who moved to
OL,12,FLeicester in 1993, I was impressed
OL,13,Fwith the close links that existed
OL,14,Fbetween the two communities.
OL,16,FI soon made friends with people from
OL,17,Fall backgrounds, and to this day, one
OL,18,Fof my closest friends is a Pakistani
OL,19,FMuslim.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
