OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1771967127
OL,3,CHow 2022's 'alarming' unrest shook
OL,4,CLeicester's proud harmony
OL,6,FIt's a well-worn phrase, but we do
OL,7,Factually have far more in common than
OL,8,Fthat which divides us.
OL,10,FThat's why the violence and unrest of
OL,11,FSeptember 2022 was so shocking. It
OL,12,Fcame as a bolt out of the blue and was
OL,13,Falarming because I hadn't seen
OL,14,Fanything like it before, and
OL,15,Fthankfully, since.
OL,17,FIt was also incredibly disappointing
OL,18,Fand sad because this wasn't the
OL,19,FLeicester I knew.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
