OL,3,CHow 2022's 'alarming' unrest shook
OL,4,CLeicester's proud harmony
OL,6,FI've heard countless explanations for
OL,7,Fwhat sparked the ugly scenes.
OL,9,FWhile residents, community leaders and
OL,10,Facademics have different theories,
OL,11,Fthere is a consensus on one crucial
OL,12,Fpoint - misinformation and fake news
OL,13,Fspread like wildfire.
OL,15,FSocial media was used to manipulate
OL,16,Fand create narratives that were
OL,17,Fdangerous and hugely destructive.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
