CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1771967127
OL,3,CHow 2022's 'alarming' unrest shook
OL,4,CLeicester's proud harmony
OL,6,FThe end result? Mindless vandalism and
OL,7,Fchaos. I was relieved and pleased that
OL,8,Fin the days which followed, community
OL,9,Fleaders acted swiftly to calm tensions
OL,10,Fand appeal for calm.
OL,12,FFor the people who call Leicester
OL,13,Ftheir home, the focus is now on
OL,14,Ffinding lasting solutions, ensuring
OL,15,Fwhat happened in September 2022 never
OL,16,Fhappens again.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/7
